5 A BILL
6 TO BE ENTITLED
7 AN ACT
8
9 Relating to the Alcoholic Beverage Control Board; to
10 amend Section 28-3A-7, Code of Alabama 1975, to further
11 provide for the importation of alcoholic beverages by
12 recognizing that a person licensed by the board to import
13 alcoholic beverages may import alcoholic beverages
14 manufactured anywhere outside of the state; to alter the
15 administrative licensure year for importers; to amend Section
16 28-3-1, Code of Alabama 1975, to make conforming changes; to
17 amend Section 28-12-45, Code of Alabama 1975, added by Act
18 2025-385, 2025 Regular Session, to authorize persons permitted
19 as a specialty retailer of electronic nicotine delivery
20 systems to obtain a consumable hemp product retailer license;
21 and to delete duplicative language and make nonsubstantive,
22 technical revisions to update the existing code language to
23 current style.
24 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
